{"tid":429272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習總香港夢】港青年自認中國人 跌至3.1%新低","createTime":"2017-10-08T17:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T04:47:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":103,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c81a960f49864332fa2ed94a068a8da59eaf3f13","tid":429272,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171008/large/1507465128_c9ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171008%2Flarge%2F1507465128_c9ee.png&h=8193cf79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平2012年十八大後開始掌權，也是特首梁振英5年任期開始。過去5年不論北京還是港府，均全力硬推愛國主義、打擊本土及港獨，但5年下來，港人對中國人身份認同並無上升，年輕人對中國人身份認同更是跌至谷底。<br />\n<br />\n港大民意研究計劃每半年調查港人身份認同。5年前習近平和梁振英分別成為中國和香港的第一把手時，自認為廣義上的中國人，意思是自認為中國人或香港的中國人中，30歲以下的年輕人有近14%。 <br />\n高位達17.5%<br />\n<br />\n自2012年中起打後兩年，有關數介乎11%至15%之間，直到2014年下旬，即佔領運動尾聲之際，年輕人中國人身份認同升至17.5%的5年高位，一般相信與當時盛傳習叫停梁開槍對付示威者，部份年輕人未對北京太反感有關。<br />\n<br />\n可是自梁於2015年借發表施政報告狠批港大學生會刊物《學苑》，繼而掀起反港獨運動後，年輕人對中國認同感不斷下跌。 2015年6月調查，僅13%年輕人自認為中國人，一年後跌至8.5%，到今年6月再下挫至僅3.1%。與此同時，自認為廣義香港人，即表示自己是香港人或中國的香港人的年輕人，由梁振英上場後的85%，攀升至今年6月的93.7%。<br />\n<br />\n相對而言，30歲以上人士自認為廣義上中國人的比例，過去5年間都在33%至43%之間上落，而自認為廣義上香港人的比例，則在54%至64%之間徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n記者 呂浩然  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171008/large/1507466781_5627.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171008%2Flarge%2F1507466781_5627.png&h=bf33ebe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171009/57306673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171009%2F57306673&d=GGkYHCSLLDUlLL8Sja8vw0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d95c0a60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171009%2F57306673&h=60a702f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171009/57306673</a>"},{"pid":"ee30f7dfd3b6372968cc3350895fdd908bfaf067","tid":429272,"uid":147541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:42:51.000Z","msg":"廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef789648cb323ec7ff4fcc5adb8fa2867f2a9af","tid":429272,"uid":19557,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:44:29.000Z","msg":"但係廢中仲係好穩定"},{"pid":"3d1fcb44f53626be76265b3aade59f7dfe8a76e6","tid":429272,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:46:36.000Z","msg":"30以上自認中國人果D根本就係投建制果堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c0973df1745a936c2a81a96b02bf013eef0cf4","tid":429272,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"中國的香港人<br />\n香港的中國人<br />\n有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">小弟無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"eb7972835acc8928b886b0c673c122c93ab5e7b8","tid":429272,"uid":45158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:51:34.000Z","msg":"唔係植入咗一大堆蝗虫咩? 佢地唔會唔認喎"},{"pid":"c866f8f276f98164d1a64596a7052cf4a3686013","tid":429272,"uid":22858,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國的香港人<br />\n香港的中國人<br />\n有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">小弟無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n用美國做例子即係<br />\nChinese American<br />\nAmerican Chinese"},{"pid":"878e08799ad86ea208953a99d33557a9c0d7acb0","tid":429272,"uid":19557,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係植入咗一大堆蝗虫咩? 佢地唔會唔認喎</blockquote><br />\n老老豆豆同過一d 新移民中學生溝通 佢地都好